    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are documented at level 1 and are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. NIH predictions demonstrate RH < 1 at all 5 operating points with mean absolute error of 8.3%, within acceptable bounds for a Class II device credibility submission. The overall evidence package is judged sufficient to support the COU decision that CFD can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device.",
